            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I'm not sure if this enable-pattern is here to stay (probably not, I imagine ui2 become the default). If it is, I would like to see the form change to:\n\n```\nrequire('vim._core.ui2').enable(enable?, opts?)\n```\n\nOr otherwise a \n\n```\nui2.config(opts?)\n```\n\nIf it can't be enabled/disabled in future versions. ",
